c: 20
v: 130
t: Teuma narit jih bek that tapapah Peue nyang jipeugah beu that tasaba Teusbeh tabaca tapujoe Allah Pujoe Po gata yoh mantong shuboh Mata uroe goh hu meujeureulah Meunan pih seupot goh jilop uroe Beu sabe laloe tapujoe Allah Takheun teuseubeh uroe ngon malam Jeuet gata seunang hana le sosah